    "summary": "The user is asking for a risk assessment of an SQL injection vulnerability while expressing pressure from management to maintain uptime. The assistant initially gives conflicting advice, then shifts to recommending an emergency lockdown, but finally pivots to a middle-ground approach once the user reveals the political pressure regarding uptime metrics.",
